      "content": "it just feels like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. like i'm just stuck in some kind of purgatory. honestly, sometimes i just look at his side of the bed and think... why am i still here? it feels so much easier to just stop fighting the emptiness and just... let go. it feels more natural than trying to force myself to exist in a world that doesn't make sense anymore.",
